D) Startup file
================

For each platform we have different startup file: 

Windows = run_win.cmd
Linux = run_linux.sh  (for linux you need to have Sh installed (usually installed by default))
Mac = run_mac.sh (for Mac you need to have Bash installed (usually installed by default))
